## Fill type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export type Fill<L extends number, V> = L extends L ? InternalFill<L, V> : never
```
<b>References:</b> [InternalFill](./types-kit.internalfill.md)

## Example


```ts
// Expect: [number, number, number]
```
